Package: simscaleR
Type: Package
Title: Large Scale Similarity Matrix Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Yizhar (Izzy)", 
    family = "Toren", 
    email = "ytoren+cran@gmail.com", role=c('cre','aut'),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4484-3811")
    )
Maintainer: Yizhar (Izzy) Toren <ytoren+cran@gmail.com>
Description: Similarity matrix calculations tools: 
    * Thresholds & sparsity: The ability to add a minimal similarity threshold and store sparse structures (instead of the full dense similarity matrix).
    * Smarter parallel calculations: Control over the distribution of the calculation, with automatic resource estimation (beta) to help use memory/CPUs efficiently.
    * Domain knowledge "injection": How to combine external information on sets of items that belong to a higher-level entity.
